{"tid":1922664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民建聯速入","createTime":"2020-03-12T16:35:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T16:39:12.000Z","uid":160912,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fb5c80825b84fc988a9249a0b52db19d29c8b3fb","tid":1922664,"uid":160912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T16:35:04.000Z","msg":"得罪個句,如果我係投開民建聯, 我寧揀Ann姐都唔要李慧琼, 理由下面再講<br />\n<br />\n首先, Ann姐作風敢怒敢言, 對基層真心上心, 但反觀李慧琼小心眼、機心算盡, 根本唔係為市民。成場武漢肺炎疫情想問下李慧琼出左幾多次聲? 最記得佢出黎請願話要每人派一萬，點知轉頭抗疫基金帶黨員投反對票, 真係老豆老母都屌左出聲, 咁既時勢仲要計住計住選票得失。就算你話佢同政府傾好左, 財政預算案派, 屌你老味個時我買口罩都買到訓街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反觀Ann姐, 雖然佢提出蒸口罩好似好反智, 但佢就係急基層所急, 先無反覆驗證就講左出黎。你可以話佢on9, 但透過佢依個舉止更加證明到佢個人係民生&gt;&gt;&gt;政治。無口罩就要諗方法嫁啦, 唔通坐係到會有口罩咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再講, Ann姐夠膽係立法會屌鳩個政府做唔到野, 唔似民建聯其他細細力屌下就算, 怕得罪政府。大佬啊, 做議員係要發表有用既野, 做算建制派都唔一定只可以為政府護航, 講大聲少少都驚既不如唔好做議員, 死去做公務員啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔同黨內比, 同工聯會比就更加不堪入目, 成個民建聯淨係諗住出豉油, 叫政府嘔隻雞出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講左咁多日民建聯班左幾多垃圾口罩, 全部薄撚過個condom, 日日就係到屌政府要派口罩, 派下派下CSI都比撚埋佢, 嘴遁真係世界第一。不過又難怪, 民建聯假假地都最大建制派, 政府要拉攏都無可口非, 但真係養懶晒d人囉, 成個黨都想坐食山崩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢對家工聯會就唔同級數, 人地自己比錢起口罩廠, 嘩真係又出豉油又出雞。真係不得不講一句, 果然有歷史係唔同d, 對番香港人都好d。真係諗唔明, 兩個黨都係女人執政, 但一個為人民服務, 另一個就城府咁深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再睇落兩個黨既第二把交椅直頭高下立見, 一個係啊bill, 一個係啊頂。前者脫韁野馬, 有自己台形(真心紋完個眉有晒氣勢), 最緊要係政績突出, 當年為左孕婦權益自己醜化自己大埋肚都肯; 但反觀後者啊頂就成個未戒奶既小朋友咁, 著住套西裝都成日要李慧琼臭住咁, 一樣政績都諗唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n綜合上述觀點, 我想同大家講一句, 民建聯快d交番建制派最大黨出黎比工聯會, 9月記住投我娟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ed3dd1f14af126ac17f214067bf88e5a681e1a1","tid":1922664,"uid":160912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T16:35:34.000Z","msg":"希望民建聯黨員睇到"},{"pid":"d2330988e9a76cc767fe377246dff78e93a93d81","tid":1922664,"uid":160912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T16:35:49.000Z","msg":"然後轉會去工聯會"},{"pid":"24fe02289bbabef081cea4cc9cd9cfcc9ca1ef2b","tid":1922664,"uid":160912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T16:36:01.000Z","msg":"工"},{"pid":"ffa4035027e64bb8df0992c0982d59fd021208fb","tid":1922664,"uid":160912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T16:36:13.000Z","msg":"聯"},{"pid":"c39365230bd8c7ef4a4e5b750d855a5af8153245","tid":1922664,"uid":160912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T16:36:24.000Z","msg":"會"},{"pid":"803d27e678abf423427be504a9741e76042be22a","tid":1922664,"uid":160912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T16:36:35.000Z","msg":"世"},{"pid":"4990fd3aeca185d644877bb66efa407b20f082a0","tid":1922664,"uid":160912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T16:36:45.000Z","msg":"界"},{"pid":"b8fd80bdf34a68073bfa348151dab5a8b80898f1","tid":1922664,"uid":160912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T16:36:55.000Z","msg":"第"},{"pid":"c020f6d1432ecfbe314c5047de8b16c683fa9f7b","tid":1922664,"uid":160912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T16:37:05.000Z","msg":"一"},{"pid":"08c63e7428a573145d20f92f913597bccd4b1837","tid":1922664,"uid":160912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T16:38:00.000Z","msg":"手足今次真係要踢走民建聯"},{"pid":"eb68298b6df8ddf7c0c952d94fd1241da540ee83","tid":1922664,"uid":160912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T16:38:42.000Z","msg":"民建聯識唔識整炸彈"},{"pid":"a33086f2775d5cacb077b60a4366ec34d93f7cbc","tid":1922664,"uid":160912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T16:38:57.000Z","msg":"原來十連咁易"},{"pid":"e0371dbe1a79193fa8e3797e461ac640af0778e5","tid":1922664,"uid":160912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T16:39:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}